Package de.thkoeln.bibl.api.rfid.tag.data

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CRC16
    Class implements the CRC-16 checksum used to verify the tag data model.
    DDMData
    Class extends the basic tag data with the specific DDM (Daenisches Daten Modell).
    DDMDataBibliotheca
    Class implements Bibliotheca's non standard implementation of the DDM and supports Bibliotheca's specific extended tag data.
    TagData
    Class represents the data of a tag and implements methods to manipulate this data.
